</section><section class="r-about-section"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer r-container-700 w-container"><div><p id="About" class="r-large-para">I'm Rachael, a <strong>Product Design Engineering graduate</strong>, with over 20 years of experience at <strong>tech startups</strong> &amp; <strong>ad agencies</strong>, creating &amp; delivering <strong>successful products </strong>based on thorough user research &amp; testing. Currently using Claude Code to design &amp; build - fast!<br><br>I recently completed my PWA app <a href="https://www.ticklists.com/" target="_blank" class="r-large-para-link">TickLists</a>, and before that was Principal Designer for <a href="https://rachaelpage.com/project/terra-app" target="_blank" class="r-large-para-link">Terra Listens</a>. Currently considering new opportunities - get in touch!</p><div class="spacer _32"></div><div class="button-group"><a href="mailto:artfulydesign@gmail.com?subject=Enquiry%20from%20your%20portfolio" class="r-button-white-on-black w-button" target="_top">Email me</a><a href="#" class="r-button-black-on-white w-button" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('artfulydesign@gmail.com');this.textContent='Copied!';setTimeout(()=>this.textContent='Copy Email',2000);return false;">Copy Email</a></div></div><div class="spacer _128"></div></div></section><section class="r-logos"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6544e287b8bf3aa40ebdb875_logos.png" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1265px) 100vw, 1265px" srcset="/images/webflow-cdn/6544e287b8bf3aa40ebdb875_logos-p-500.png 500w, /images/webflow-cdn/6544e287b8bf3aa40ebdb875_logos-p-800.png 800w, /images/webflow-cdn/6544e287b8bf3aa40ebdb875_logos-p-1080.png 1080w, /images/webflow-cdn/6544e287b8bf3aa40ebdb875_logos.png 1265w" alt="Logos of companies and clients Rachael Page has worked with" decoding="async"></section><section id="Work" data-wf--r-work--variant-without-title="homepage" class="r-work"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-1225 w-container"><div class=