e="opacity: 1;" decoding="async"><div class="div-block-108"><h4 class="r-h3">Ticklists App</h4><div class="div-block-109"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/65425e3532e0c196bde9cbfe_R-Arrow right.svg" loading="lazy" width="23" height="20" alt="" class="image-40" decoding="async"></div></div><div class="r-body">PWA (Progressive Web App) for shared repetitive shopping &amp; routines. See only the things your household/team needs to buy in exactly the right walking order for any store &amp; in routines, only todays outstanding tasks</div><div class="spacer _64"></div><div class="spacer _16"></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="r-work-others"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer r-container-no-padd w-container"><div><div class="w-dyn-list"><div role="list" class="w-dyn-items w-row"><div role="listitem" class="w-dyn-item w-col w-col-6"><a href="/rachael-page/project/terra-app" class="link-block-12 w-inline-block"><img alt="" loading="lazy" data-w-id="817dc4d1-a2a5-f621-402e-1f1f2a85d8b3" src="/images/webflow-cdn/68a5e7984df7a15a836e8c16_Animation full width terra app.gif" alt="Terra Listens native app — animated UI design by Rachael Page" class="r-work-image-feature" decoding="async"><div class="div-block-108"><h4 class="r-h4-small">Terra Listens Native Apps</h4><div class="div-block-109"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/65425e3532e0c196bde9cbfe_R-Arrow right.svg" loading="lazy" width="23" height="20" alt="" class="image-40" decoding="async"></div></div><div class="r-body">Streaming nature sounds from gardens &amp; global birding hotpots with live bird ID's</div><div class="spacer _64"></div></a></div><div role="listitem" class="w-dyn-item w-col w-col-6"><a href="/rachael-page/project/mcdonalds-monopoly-mobile-site" class="link-block-12 w-inline-block"><img alt="" loading="lazy" data-w-id="817dc4d1-a2a5-f621-402e-1f1f2a85d8b3" src="/images/webflow-cdn/McDonalds thumb.gif" alt="McDonald's Monopoly mobile web app — UX design by Rachael Page" class="r-work-image-feature" decoding="async"><div class="div-block-108"><h4 class="r-h4-small">McDonalds Monopoly Web-App</h4><div class="div-block-109"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/65425e3532e0c196bde9cbfe_R-Arrow right.svg" loading="lazy" width="23" height="20" alt="" class="image-40" decoding="async"></div></div><div class="r-body">Complex UX Design for this Mobile-first game: the first year it went mobile in Australia</div><div class="spacer _64"></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="Skills" class="r-skills"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-1228 w-container"><div class="r-div-line-top"><h3 class="r-h2 left">Skills</h3></div><div class="div-block-107"><div id="w-node-e08c51c3-2efd-0439-acdb-4e7df15743b1-5d036c99"><h4 id="w-node-_55bcc439-dc83-fb71-d633-c3290ff723fb-5d036c99" class="r-body">Claude Code<br>Claude Design<br>Agentic AI (Claude)<br>Figma<br>Adobe Photoshop<br>Adobe Illustrator<br>Adobe After Effects<br>DaVinci Resolve<br>Jitter.video<br>Discord &amp; Midjourney<br>Webflow<br>V0.dev &amp; Lovable &amp; Replit<br>Asana<br>Many online tools &amp; plugins</h4></div><div id="w-node-a537fab4-e251-02ff-455c-cd6eabe5e900-5d036c99"><h4 id="w-node-a537fab4-e251-02ff-455c-cd6eabe5e901-5d036c99" class="r-body">Product Design<br>UX Design<br>UI Design<br>User Research<br>User Testing<br>Project Management &amp; hiring<br>Information Architectures<br>Marketing<br>Conversion Funnel Design<br>Product Strategy<br>Marketing Strategy<br>Graphic &amp; Packaging Design<br>Responsive Development<br>Teaching Design</h4></div><div id="w-node-d13601b3-7b98-33ec-c60a-e18e8ab58266-5d036c99"><h4 id="w-node-d13601b3-7b98-33ec-c60a-e18e8ab58267-5d036c99" class="r-body">Native App &amp; Web-App Design<br>Motion Design<br>Mobile-first Design<br>Competitive Analysis<br>User Surveys<br>User Research, Testing &amp; Analysis<br>Personas<br>Concept Ideation<br>User Flows &amp; Journeys<br>Clickable Wireframes/Prototypes<br>SEO Research &amp; Copywriting<br>Branding &amp; Logos<br>HTML &amp; CSS</h4></div><div id="w-node-d5140b0f-3487-482b-c12d-6e876614e9ad-5d036c99" class="r-div-hp-skills"><h4 id="w-node-d5140b0f-3487-482b-c12d-6e876614e9ae-5d036c99" class="r-h4">Software</h4></div><div id="w-node-ece15462-397b-9dc5-70d4-150d930c6c01-5d036c99"><h4 id="w-node-ece15462-397b-9dc5-70d4-150d930c6c02-5d036c99" class="r-h4">Knowledge</h4></div><div id="w-node-_3e42c28a-363a-aa0b-7094-b08b882547a8-5d036c99" class="div-block-118"><h4 id="w-node-_3e42c28a-363a-aa0b-7094-b08b882547a9-5d036c99" class="r-h4">Deliverables</h4></div></div></div></section><div id="w-node-_85b8d66e-8852-6d0b-31cb-a85dc5b1dd96-5d036c99" class="spacer _64"></div><section class="r-experience-section"><div class="page-padding"><div class="container-large-2"><div class="layout-12-column"><div id="w-node-_4f13231d-e5b2-7c9a-ae9a-f198260a7151-5d036c99" class="sticky-title-wrapper"><div class="section-title is-offset"><h2 class="r-h2 left">Experience</h2></div></div><div id="w-node-_4f13231d-e5b2-7c9a-ae9a-f198260a7155-5d036c99" class="content-wrapper"><div class="r-div-block-experience"><div class="r-body">CURRENT<br><strong><em>Seeking new opportunities<br></em></strong>Designing and building <a href="https://rachaelpage.com/work/native-apps-pwas" class="r-body-link">apps</a> with Claude. Marketing <a href="https://www.amazon.com/author/rachael-page" target="_blank" class="r-body-link">my books</a> and apps, plus <a href="https://rachaelpage.com/work/graphic-design" class="r-body-link">surface pattern design</a> for Spoonflower.<br>‍<br>Jan 2022 - Dec 2024<br><a href="https://rachaelpage.com/project/terra-app" class="r-body-link">Terra Listens,</a> <a href="https://careerfoundry.com/" target="_blank" class="r-body-link">Career Foundry</a> &amp; <a href="https://www.artfuly.com/" target="_blank" class="r-body-link">Artfuly</a><br><em>Product Designer &amp; Design Educator</em><br>Design &amp; develop Terra Listen's digital roadmap. Teaching UX &amp; Product Design, writing Design courses and holding online events<br><br>Sep 2021 - Dec 2022<br><a href="https://kpmg.com/uk/en/home.html" target="_blank" class="r-body-link">KPMG</a> &amp; <a href="https://www.pwc.co.uk/" target="_blank" class="r-body-link">PWC</a>, London<br><em>Freelance UX Researcher &amp; UI Designer</em><br>Via <a href="https://theplaystudio.com/" target="_blank" class="r-body-link">Play Studio</a> in London I worked as a user researcher for KPMG UK and PWC UK <br><br>Jan 2012-2020<br><a href="https://rachaelpage.com/project/artfuly-original-art-marketplace" class="r-body-link">Artfuly,</a> Online<br><em>Founder, Head of UX &amp; Product</em><br>A global art marketplace where artists could market &amp; sell artworks with delivery door to door<br><br>Nov 2016 - Jul 2017<br><a href="https://www.amcor.com/" target="_blank" class="r-body-link">Amcor</a>, Zurich<br><em>Snr. UX Consultant</em><br>Redesign of the Amcor.com products section, including stakeholder interviews, user research, product database design, clickable prototype / wireframes and visual design. Included working for <a href="https://tzuand.co/" target="_blank" class="link-39">Tzu&amp;Co</a> for the same and other clients<br><br>Oct 2015 - Jun 2016<br><a href="https://www.sydney.edu.au/" target="_blank" class="r-body-link">Sydney University,</a> Australia<br><em>Lead UX (Contract)</em><br>User research and design for Sydney University. A high-profile project, in 2014 the University’s income from students alone was $760 Million AUD<br><br>2004 - 2012<br><span class="r-body-bold">Several top Ad Agencies</span><a href="https://www.sydney.edu.au/" target="_blank" class="r-body-link"><span class="r-body-bold">, </span></a><br><em>Australia<br>Snr. UI/UX Designer (Contract)</em><br>Working on Mobile app, podium touchscreen, responsive website designs<br>‍<br><a href="mailto:artfulydesign@gmail.com?subject=Request%20a%20copy%20of%20CV" class="r-body-link" target="_top">For full experience history, please request a copy of my CV</a>‍<br></div><div class="spacer _128"></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="r-qualif-section"><div class="page-padding"><div class="container-large-2"><div class="layout-12-column"><div id="w-node-_4d9e1f65-3a15-5c0e-8546-3924935379ab-5d036c99" class="sticky-title-wrapper"><div class="section-title is-offset"><h2 class="r-h2 left">Qualifications</h2></div></div><div id="w-node-_4d9e1f65-3a15-5c0e-8546-3924935379af-5d036c99" class="content-wrapper"><div class="r-div-block-qual"><div class="r-body"><a href="https://www.awardschool.com.au/" target="_blank"><strong>Award School</strong><br></a>Australian Writers &amp; Art Directors<br><br><strong>Adobe Creative Suite</strong><br><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/colinseton/" target="_blank">Hypermouse</a><br><br><a href="https://www.lboro.ac.uk/study/undergraduate/courses/product-design-engineering-beng/" target="_blank"><strong>Bachelor of Engineering (Honours) in Product Design</strong></a><br>Loughborough University, UK<br></div><div class="spacer _32"></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section-68"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-1248 w-container"><div id="w-node-_7aee0af0-0fed-5f7a-08c9-224e519a1611-5d036c99" class="div-block-144"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/A Rachael Page full length crop v2.png" loading="lazy" id="w-node-_2bbfc82d-7ae7-07bd-f0ce-65cb7ae86c44-5d036c99" alt="Rachael Page, Product Designer" class="image-51" decoding="async"></div><div id="w-node-d3f9494b-72c7-f7b6-2fd7-d0e4d05f45a0-5d036c99" class="div-unique"><h3 class="heading-hp-unique">What makes me unique</h3></div><div id="w-node-_62658785-10ae-d1d8-61f0-8b9c39a17398-5d036c99"><div class="r-body"><strong>Diverse Expertise:</strong> I have a rare blend of product design, UX research, and leadership experience across industries, from startups to blue-chip brands.</div></div><div id="w-node-c1eb4d4e-b350-6230-7eb7-e9b0e1ec9682-5d036c99"><div class="r-body"><strong>Tech &amp; Design Fusion:</strong> I combine technical knowledge with high-quality UX and visual design, building responsive digital products with HTML, CSS, Webflow and now Claude Code.</div></div><div id="w-node-e96fe20c-198a-c14c-d228-742e0d2b1a98-5d036c99"><div class="r-body"><strong>Business Acumen &amp; Critical Thinking:</strong> Founding and managing my own startups and working with several other startups, highlights my end-to-end skills in <strong><em>product concept ideation</em></strong>, design, and execution.</div></div><div id="w-node-bd2e293f-9f7f-2b52-35f0-5d7471788ef9-5d036c99"><div class="r-body"><strong>Global Impact:</strong> My career spans multiple countries, industries, and remote roles, reflecting adaptability and global relevance.</div></div><div id="w-node-b9801143-b179-f32a-9c1d-43a228c0d239-5d036c99" class="div-unique-item"><div class="r-body"><strong>Speed &amp; Attention to detail:</strong> I continuously upgrade my wide skillset, and use agentic AI for optimum efficiency.</div></div></div></section><section class="r-testimonials"><section class="section_testimonial17"><div class="padding-global"><div class="container-large"><div class="padding-section-large"><div class="margin-bottom margin-xxlarge"><div class="text-align-center"><div class="max-width-large align-center"><div class="margin-bottom margin-small"><h2 class="r-h2-testimonials">Testimonials</h2></div><p class="text-size-medium">References available on request</p></div></div></div><div class="testimonial17_component"><div class="testimonial17_content"><div class="margin-bottom margin-small"><div class="testimonial17_rating-wrapper"><div class="div-block-stars"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"></div></div><div class="r-block-quote">Rachael has been my secret weapon when it comes to design. &nbsp;<br>Her many years of professional work, her keen aesthetic sense, and her ability to put focus on what’s important at the right time have made a tremendous difference.<br><br>Thanks to Rachael, we have a valuable new app for the business that is a cornerstone to our success. I’m lucky to have found someone who is both in my corner and able to help me express my vision to the world.</div></div><div class="testimonial17_client"><div class="testimonial17_client-info"><p class="text-weight-semibold"><strong class="text-weight-semibold">Scott Whittle, <br>Terra CEO</strong></p><p class="city-country-date"><strong class="city-country-date">Cape May NJ, USA</strong></p></div></div></div><div class="testimonial17_content"><div class="margin-bottom margin-small"><div class="testimonial17_rating-wrapper"><div class="div-block-stars"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"></div></div><div class="r-block-quote">Rachael reworked our existing B2B tool's UX and expanded on it. The services offered are complex and there were many legacy parameters to contend with. <br><br>Rachael came up with a much improved flow, she is not afraid of questioning the status quo to get the best outcome for the user, and the outcome is a much more user friendly and scalable UX. I would happily employ Rachael again</div></div><div class="testimonial17_client"><div class="testimonial17_client-info"><p class="text-weight-semibold"><strong>Margaret Sliman, <br>Inivio Manager</strong></p><p class="city-country-date">Sydney, AU</p></div></div></div><div class="testimonial17_content"><div class="margin-bottom margin-small"><div class="testimonial17_rating-wrapper"><div class="div-block-stars"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"><img src="/images/webflow-cdn/6599744d887272af544d4af0_Teal star.svg" loading="lazy" width="25" height="25" alt="" class="star" decoding="async"></div></div><div class="r-block-quote">Rachael is a very professional and capable UX Designer with a strong business and entrepreneurial mindset. <br><br>When she worked onsite for my client she performed what she was asked to do, to a very high standard, and left the project in a much stronger condition than when she first joined. <br><br>I can strongly recommend Rachael for any position that requires UI/IA wire-framing etc<br></div></div><div class="testimonial17_client"><div class="testimonial17_client-info"><p class="text-weight-semibold"><strong>Matthew Drake, Recruiter</strong></p><p class="city-country-date">Sydney, AU</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="spacer _128"></div></section></section><section class="r-pubs"><section class="section_pubs"><div class="padding-global"><div class="container-large"><div class="padding-section-large"><div class="margin-bottom margin-xxlarge"><div class="text-align-center"><div class="max-width-large align-center"><div class="margin-bottom margin-small"><h2 class="r-h2-testimonials">Books &amp; Articles</h2></div><p class="text-size-medium"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/author/rachael-page" target="_blank" class="link-47">Published Books</a> and my Articles published here and on other websites</p></div></div></div><div class="pubs_component"><div class="pubs_content-folio-hp-articles"><div class="margin-bottom margin-small"><div class="w-dyn-list"><div role="list" class="collection-list-folio-hp-articles w-dyn-items w-row rp-articles-grid" style={`--article-cols: ${articleCols}`}>
